job.description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The Solutions Architecture team is the backbone that helps the go-to-market (GTM) team run effectively. Our job is to manage the full funnel operations across the customer lifecycle and provide the organization documentation and expertise needed for the teams to function efficiently.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;This Solutions Architecture leader is responsible for creating and implementing strategies that improve global operations across our revenue organization. We measure success by your accuracy, speed, and ability to build out processes and infrastructure to drive hiring, team enablement and support sales team activities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In one year you’ll know you were successful if you…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Created and implemented solutions to drive and retain revenue by collaborating with teams such as sales, marketing, and customer success and training&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Surfaced insights, business analytics, and data across all GTM functions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Identified bottlenecks and collaborated with leadership/enablement to proactively unblock growth&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Optimized our sales strategy, enablement, and execution as a whole&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Defined the analytics framework to measure individual and company performance and owned the end-to-end process of tracking and analyzing the sales funnel from lead to customer&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Created models for lead, company, and deal scoring. Designed a strategy for enrichment, attribution modeling, and campaign measurement&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Managed the tech stack of the GTM organization. Owned the recommendation, selection, and deployment of new technologies and tools to scale the GTM organization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A background like this helps:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
