&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong working knowledge of the tools we use (or similar) to run the business and the ability to quickly learn and optimize new technologies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have very strong Salesforce reporting, dashboarding, and workflow skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
