&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Be the voice of the Luno corporate brand across all relevant social media channels. You will be our brand’s voice on all things crypto and Luno in order to drive an increase in corporate brand awareness through thought leadership, position Luno as an employer of choice, and maintain healthy online relationships with press and news contacts.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
