&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner with global and local stakeholders to help craft the content calendar for the channels in your remit, manage publishing across these channels, and compile regular and ad hoc social media reports on wins &amp;amp; misses.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Share best practices across your team as a senior member of the team, exploring new tools and processes, helping to develop efficient workflow.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Manage the social engagement team as a maternity cover, and generally serve as a team 2iC.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
