&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with the GCP suite, including BigQuery, Composer, and Cloud Functions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interest in and proficiency with blockchain solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for video games&lt;/li&gt;
