&lt;li&gt;Help set the experimentation roadmap in partnership with research, data, product teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use empirical and experimental data to improve the design of our data products, inventory management, and pricing operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inform broad strategic and product direction by estimating and applying structural models of supply and demand to evaluate the general equilibrium effects of business decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate effectively with senior management and counterparts across the organization&lt;/li&gt;
