&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Our network consists of closely aligned teams, products, and organizations. We’re committed to building the open web: a transformed, decentralized digital world in which each creator and community benefits, not just a few companies. We believe that blockchain technology is a major piece of that transformation, and we work together to connect builders with mentors, solutions, capital—and each other.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
