&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;It’s not just about providing capital; it’s about scaling venture solutions by providing value-added support, piloting, and partnership opportunities to startups in our portfolio and pipeline. For early-stage companies, we focus on business fundamentals, management, and product-market fit. For later-stage companies, it’s all about growth, expansion, and deepening impact.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The Director, Founder Lab provides strategic guidance and leadership to our venture building services. The Director, Founder Lab is the leader for the venture building support and resources globally and has a deep understanding of technology, startups, entrepreneurship, and venture capital.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities &amp;amp; Deliverables:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
