&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Paxos is on a mission to enable the movement of any asset, any time, in a trustworthy way. Today’s financial infrastructure is archaic, expensive, inefficient and risky - supporting a system that leaves out more people than it lets in. So we’re rebuilding it.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;As a regulated blockchain infrastructure company, we use technology to tokenize, custody, trade, and settle assets for enterprise clients like PayPal, Novi, Bank of America, and Interactive Brokers. Paxos is a top-funded blockchain company, with more than $500 million in total funding from leading investors like OakHC/FT, Founders Fund, PayPal Ventures, and Declaration Partners. Together, we empower today’s financial leaders to build a more open, trusted economy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The Paxos&lt;strong&gt; Securities&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;business&lt;/strong&gt; is expanding its team and needs business development experts to help drive change in the industry. Reporting to the head of business development for Securities, this role will own selling into and leading strategic client and partner relationships.The ideal candidate will have experience selling enterprise technology and owning relationships with complex organizations, as well as a strong interest in driving the adoption of the Paxos financial market infrastructure to replace the legacy infrastructure used today.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As a Business Development Officer, you&#39;ll get to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
