&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A track record of building customer relationships in large enterprises while delivering on commercial goals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
