&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Figure is looking for a Head of Investor Relations to lead our company vision and strategy for delivering shareholder value.&amp;nbsp; If you are looking for an opportunity to develop and create a robust investor relations strategy from the ground floor, this role is for you.&amp;nbsp; This role will require a corporate professional who also has entrepreneurial skills and looks to the future with optimism to envision what could be possible.&amp;nbsp; Success in this role will require collaboration, communication, leadership and vision.&amp;nbsp; A driven, self-starter who is confident in taking responsibility and taking projects to completion with minimal guidance will be successful in this role. The successful candidate will engage, develop, and maintain positive interactions with the investment community on behalf of Figure.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop investor confidence and belief in Figure’s vision and strategy for delivering shareholder value&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
