&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Establish and enforce security standards for adoption and integration with SaaS and cloud-based solutions; ensure CUECs are fully implemented.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
